Welcome to MyPolice-Belgium, the official app of the Belgian Integrated Police, designed to facilitate contacts and exchange of information between the Belgian Integrated Police and the public.

Download MyPolice-Belgium for free and enjoy this official app provided by the Belgian Federal Police.

Discover MyPolice-Belgium:
- police zones: find information about the police zones of your choice wherever you are;
- news: check local and federal news easily;
- wanted persons: help find a fugitive or a missing person;
- online reporting: find in a single click the various types of reports that can be filed online;
- work for the police: easy access to the «jobpol.be» recruitment site;
- emergency numbers: check and dial the right number directly.

The little perk of this app? It helps you find police stations nearby when you choose to turn on location on your phone.

Download MyPolice-Belgium and discover this new app for the public. You will also have the possibility to pass on your remarks to enhance the app so that it best suits your wishes and needs!


Use of cookies and other technologies:
- location data are not stored and are only used to find police stations nearby;
- the app works without cookies and without database, therefore not allowing storage of location data.
